issue.title: Check if today is a tracked day for LunchOutDetectionReceiver
issue.body:
In addition to making sure the wifi, start time, and end time are set, we now also check if today's day of week is tracked before proceeding with the Wifi detection.

This PR addresses https://github.com/AndroidAtelier/lunch-in/issues/66
